Title: Authorizes the superintendent of financial services to authorize the return of subscribing member operating reserve balances to members of a municipal insurance reciprocal
Summary: Authorizes the superintendent of financial services to authorize the return of subscribing member operating reserve balances to members of a municipal insurance reciprocal.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the insurance law, in relation to authorizing the superintendent of financial services to authorize the return of subscribing member operating reserve balances to members of a municipal insurance reciprocal
